text: Domeciidae is a family of crabs. ==Subfamilies and genera== The World Register of Marine Species lists the following genera: *Domecia Eydoux & Souleyet, 1842 *Jonesius Sankarankutty, 1962 *Maldivia Borradaile, 1902 *Palmyria Galil & Takeda, 1986 ==References== ==External links== * Category:Crabs
